#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:169
msgid "Holi"
msgstr "Holi"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/holi.tsx:197
msgid "Holi is a joyful festival of colour, celebrated with laughter, music, and shared community."
msgstr "Holi — džiaugsminga spalvų šventė, švenčiama su juoku, muzika ir bendryste."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/lunar-new-year.tsx:90
msgid "Homes are carefully cleaned and decorated to clear away old luck and welcome prosperity for the year ahead."
msgstr "Namai kruopščiai valomi ir puošiami, kad būtų „nušluota“ sena sėkmė ir pasitikta gerovė ateinantiems metams."

#: src/pages/feedback/index.tsx:167
#~ msgid "I would appreciate if you could provide some feedback as to why you've uninstalled Weather Please. This allows me to make Weather Please a better product."
#~ msgstr "Būčiau dėkingas, jei galėtumėte pateikti atsiliepimų, kodėl išinstaliavote Weather Please. Tai leidžia man padaryti Weather Please geresniu produktu."

#: src/components/settings/index.tsx:405
#~ msgid "I'd love to bring Weather Please to more languages."
#~ msgstr "Norėčiau atnesti Weather Please į daugiau kalbų."

#: src/features/settings/ui/settings.tsx:277
msgid "Identifier"
msgstr "Identifikatorius"

#: src/components/settings/index.tsx:206
#~ msgid "If this is incorrect, please update the values below."
#~ msgstr "Jei tai klaidinga, prašome atnaujinti žemiau esančias reikšmes."

#: src/components/settings/index.tsx:410
#~ msgid "If you have a translation request, please reach out at <0>contact@weather-please.app</0>"
