msgstr "Žiemos saulėgrįža"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/hanukkah.tsx:112
#~ msgid "With each night, a new flame appears, forming a quiet ladder of light against the dark."
#~ msgstr "Su kiekviena naktimi atsiranda nauja liepsna, sudarydama tylų šviesos laiptelį prieš tamsą."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/holi.tsx:245
